---
import '../styles/global.css';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Event Schedule | America's Biggest 250th Anniversary Ball | Washington DC July 3, 2026" description="Full schedule for America's biggest 250th anniversary gala. 4 stages, midnight countdown, 6 party zones. July 3-4, 2026, Washington Hilton, DC." ogImage="/images/event/diverse-grand-ballroom.png">
  <Navbar />
  <main>
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 bg-navy text-white overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-navy-dark/90 to-navy"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <p class="text-gold font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-4">The Evening's Events</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading">Schedule & Program</h1>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6 font-heading">Evening Overview</h2>
          <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gold mx-auto"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-slate/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 text-center">
          <p>Here's a preview of how the evening unfolds. The detailed program will be finalized closer to the event.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="relative mb-16">
          <div class="absolute left-6 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gold/30"></div>

          <div class="relative pl-16 pb-10">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-gold border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">6:30 PM</h3>
            <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">VIP & Statesman's Early Entry</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">Doors open for Patriot VIP and Statesman's Concierge Pass holders. Private expedited entrance for Statesman's guests.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16 pb-10">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-gold border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">7:00 PM</h3>
            <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">VIP Reception Begins</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">Premium buffet dinner, open bar, live entertainment, and the opportunity to mingle with honored guests, dignitaries, and All-American Heroes.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16 pb-10">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-gold border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">9:00 PM</h3>
            <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">The Ball Begins</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">Doors open for all ticket holders. 6 party zones, 4 stages, multiple bands and DJs, open bar, and immersive experiences throughout the venue.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16 pb-10">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-gold border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">10:00 PM</h3>
            <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Patriotic Tribute to America</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">A stirring patriotic performance honoring 250 years of American history.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16 pb-10">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-gold border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">11:00 PM</h3>
            <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">All-American Hero Awards Ceremony</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">The All-American Hero Lifetime Achievement Awards are presented to extraordinary Americans for their lifetime of service.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16 pb-10">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-red border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Midnight</h3>
            <p class="text-red font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">The Countdown</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">The moment we've all been waiting for — the historic midnight countdown launching America's 250th anniversary. July 4, 2026 begins!</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-16">
            <div class="absolute left-4 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-gold border-4 border-white"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">12:00 AM – 1:00 AM</h3>
            <p class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">The Celebration Continues</p>
            <p class="text-slate/60">The party continues with live music, dancing, and celebration into the early hours of America's birthday.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-navy rounded-2xl p-10 text-center">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-gold mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z" />
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gold mb-3">Full Program Coming Soon</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-lg mb-6">
            The detailed event program — including performer times, ceremony schedule, and party zone guides — will be announced as the event approaches.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Times shown above are approximate and subject to change.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/#tickets" class="inline-block bg-red hover:bg-red-light text-white px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase transition-all rounded shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            Get Your Tickets
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
